botConfig.text:
Below are all the config settings of your bot.
Use `{{ prefix }}botConfig <key>` to view a single setting
Use `{{ prefix }}botConfig <key> <value>` to set the config <key> to <value>
botConfig.canNotClear: The config setting **{{ key }}** can not be cleared. You can use `{{ prefix }}botConfig {{ key }} default` to reset it to the default value.
botConfig.notSet: Ces paramètres ne sont pas définis

current.title: Valeur actuelle
current.text:
This config is currently set.
Use `{{ prefix }}botConfig {{ key }} <value>` to change it.
Use `{{ prefix }}botConfig {{ key }} default` to reset it to the default.
current.notSet:
This config is currently **not** set.
Use `{{ prefix }}config {{ key }} <value>` to set it.
current.clear: Utilisez `{{ prefix }}botConfig {{ key }} none` pour l'effacer.

botConfig.sameValue: Cette configuration est déjà définie sur cette valeur.

Use `{{ prefix }}botConfig {{ key }} <value>` to change it again.
Use `{{ prefix }}botConfig {{ key }} default` to reset it to the default.
